		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="428" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之雷进行猜拳三连击攻击，施放石头-剪刀-布，石头和剪刀均造成<span color="#ffacff">70%</span><span>伤害，布造成</span><span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之雷只出石头，造成<span color="#ffacff">70%</span><span>伤害，随后停止攻击暴露核心。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="927" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之雷贴地高速旋转，在其周围持续造成<span color="#ffacff">25%</span><span>伤害，其顺时针施放雷晶潮，触碰造成</span><span color="#ffacff">75%</span><span>伤害，后暴露核心，并留下一个</span><span color="#ffacff">雷元素晶球</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="438" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之雷蜕去外壳，击飞并造成<span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害，其将雷柱落下，围成牢笼困锁玩家，并在其间进行雷击，雷击造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害；雷柱之间会形成屏障，触碰屏障造成</span><span color="#ffacff">1-10点</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="439" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之雷蜕去外壳，击飞并造成<span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害，雷立方围着无相之雷，发射8道逆时针旋转的激光，接触造成</span><span color="#ffacff">40%</span><span>伤害；激光施放完毕后，无相之雷剧烈收缩造成</span><span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害，并留下一个</span><span color="#ffacff">雷元素晶球</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之雷%B7协奏曲%B7紫电之光.assets/Image_15.png')" x="719" y="138">
