		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之雷%B7协奏曲%B7紫电之光.assets/Image_23.png')" x="1391" y="1065">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之雷开阵，8个雷立方围成一圈暴露核心，其依次将雷立方转化为雷球发射，雷球碰到造成<span color="#ffacff">25%</span><span>伤害，爆炸造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害，共计发射3枚雷球。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="428" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之雷将外壳化为成两面墙，随后夹击，造成<span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害。夹击时生成3个游离的雷球，碰到造成</span><span color="#ffacff">25%</span><span>伤害，爆炸造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">存在于至纯无相之雷的场地上，可被雷元素激活，激活后产生脉冲，造成<span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害，可被元素反应失活。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1151" width="434" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">生命值低于5%时，无相之雷召唤<span textDecoration="underline">3种雷棱镜</span><span>，复苏持续15s，每个雷棱镜/大雷棱镜恢复</span><span color="#ffacff">9%/12%</span><span>生命值，每</span><span color="#ffacff">1/2/3</span><span>个雷立方晶恢复</span><span color="#ffacff">6%/10%/15%</span><span>生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#8d29b4" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#8d29b4">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之雷%B7协奏曲%B7紫电之光.assets/Image_24.png')" x="596" y="171" blendMode="normal">
