		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之雷化成钻头向前突进，接触造成<span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害，若持续接触则额外再造成</span><span color="#ebe5d8">25%</span><span>伤害；技能施放完毕后会接上其他技能。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
