		<RichText x="66" y="1104" width="341" height="116" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷柱：<span color="#ffacff">4.4雷</span><span>盾，击破可破坏附近的雷屏障。<br/>电气紫晶：</span><span color="#ffacff">2雷</span><span>盾，击破可使其停用。<br/>3种雷棱镜：<br/>大雷棱方：</span><span color="#ffacff">4雷</span><span>盾，击破产生1个</span><span color="#ffacff">雷元素晶球</span><span>。<br/>雷棱镜：</span><span color="#ffacff">3雷</span><span>盾，击破2个产生1个</span><span color="#ffacff">雷元素晶球</span><span>。<br/>雷立方晶：</span><span color="#ffacff">2雷</span><span>盾，击破3个产生1个</span><span color="#ffacff">雷元素晶球</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
